<title>CSS Test: Test that a variable reference within a gradient value in a border-image shorthand parses correctly.</title><style>
</style><link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css-variables-1/#using-variables">
<style>
p {
  --orange: orange;
  border: 2px solid transparent;
  border-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--orange), blue) 1 1;
}
</style>
<link rel="match" href="variable-reference-40-ref.html">
<p>This paragraph must have an orange/blue gradient border.</p>
